PN,31101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FEleven cancers have been identified to
OL,7,Fbe on the rise in young people in the
OL,8,FUK, with rising obesity thought to be
OL,9,Fone of the key drivers.
OL,11,FFollowing a study at Imperial College
OL,12,FLondon, researchers said they believed
OL,13,Fbeing overweight or obese plays a role
OL,14,Fin the increased risk of cancer,
OL,15,Fpossibly due to increased levels of
OL,16,Finsulin and inflammation.
OL,18,FHowever, they emphasised that the true
OL,19,Fcauses are still not fully understood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
