FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FIn 2023, around 31,000 cancers were
OL,7,Fdiagnosed in people aged 20 to 49 in
OL,8,FEngland ` roughly one in 1,000 people.
OL,10,FIn contrast, far more cases (244,000)
OL,11,Fwere diagnosed in those aged 50 to 79
OL,12,F` roughly one in every 100.
OL,14,FOf the younger group, breast cancer
OL,15,Fwas most common (8,500 cases), while
OL,16,Fbowel cancer accounted for 3,000 cases
OL,17,Fand melanoma skin cancer 2,800.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FThe other cancers identified were
OL,7,Fthyroid, multiple myeloma, liver,
OL,8,Fkidney, gallbladder, pancreatic, womb
OL,9,Flining (or endometrial), mouth and
OL,10,Fovarian.
OL,12,FScientists have struggled to
OL,13,Funderstand why cancer rates in young
OL,14,Fpeople have been increasing for years.
OL,16,FThe researchers of the study pointed
OL,17,Fout that most known risk factors for
OL,18,Fthese cancers, such as smoking,
OL,19,Fdrinking alcohol, red or processed
OL,20,Fmeats, low fibre intake and lack of
OL,21,Fexercise, were generally in decline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FIn contrast, the rising number of
OL,7,Fpeople who are overweight and obese,
OL,8,Fwhich has been steadily increasing
OL,9,Fsince 1995, could be a key factor in
OL,10,Fthe jump in cases, the researchers
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FAll of the 11 cancers identified,
OL,14,Fother than oral cancer, are known to
OL,15,Fbe linked to excess weight, the
OL,16,Fresearchers said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FHowever, the study, published in the
OL,7,Fjournal BMJ Oncology, found that
OL,8,Fincreases in body mass index (BMI)
OL,9,Falone are not enough to explain the
OL,10,Foverall rise in cancer among younger
OL,11,Fadults in England.
OL,13,FThere must be other additional causes
OL,14,Ffor the rise, whether suspected causes
OL,15,For currently unknown, the team said.
OL,17,FMost cancers with rates rising in
OL,18,Fyounger adults are also increasing in
OL,19,Folder adults, suggesting there are
OL,20,Fcommon causes between the two.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FProfessor Montse Garcia-Closas, from
OL,7,Fthe ICR, said data suggested around
OL,8,F15% of bowel cancer in younger people
OL,9,Fcould be down to being overweight or
OL,10,Fobese, with around 40% to 50% in total
OL,11,Fdown to the effect of combined known
OL,12,Frisk factors such as obesity, lack of
OL,13,Fexercise, alcohol and smoking.
OL,15,FThe team suggested that between 2001
OL,16,Fand 2019, around 20% of the increase
OL,17,Fin bowel cancer was explained by the
OL,18,Fincreases in BMI over this period of
OL,19,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FProfessor Marc Gunter, from Imperial,
OL,7,Fsaid obesity is a known risk factor
OL,8,Ffor around 19 different cancers.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FHe added: "For some of these cancers,
OL,16,Fincluding colorectal (bowel) cancer,
OL,17,Fwe think this could be partly caused
OL,18,Fby higher levels of hormones such as
OL,19,Finsulin which is often elevated in
OL,20,Fpeople with obesity, as well as
OL,21,Finflammation.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,F"We know people with obesity have
OL,7,Fhigher levels of insulin, and insulin
OL,8,Fis a growth factor and has been linked
OL,9,Fto cancer.
OL,11,F"In a recent study, we actually found
OL,12,Fthat insulin in particular might be
OL,13,Fplaying a role in early onset
OL,14,Fcolorectal (bowel) cancer, and this is
OL,15,Factually an area of very active
OL,16,Fresearch at the moment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
