PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777493189
OL,3,CEleven cancers on the rise in young
OL,4,Cpeople, with obesity partially linked
OL,6,FThe researchers called for large,
OL,7,Flongterm research studies to identify
OL,8,Fall biological and environmental
OL,9,Ffactors that could explain rising
OL,10,Fcancer rates in young adults.
OL,12,FHowever, they said the case is strong
OL,13,Fenough on obesity to make it a public
OL,14,Fhealth priority, particularly driving
OL,15,Fdown obesity rates in children and
OL,16,Fyoung people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
